OL,3,CNUFC legend Shaka Hislop reveals
OL,4,C'aggressive' prostate cancer battle
OL,6,FNewcastle United legend Shaka Hislop
OL,7,Fhas revealed he has received treatment
OL,8,Ffor prostate cancer.
OL,10,FThe former Number 1 played as part of
OL,11,FKevin Keegan's 'entertainers' squad,
OL,12,Fplaying at St James' Park between 1995
OL,13,Fand 1998.
OL,15,FHe also played for teams Reading and
OL,16,FWest Ham United, and had 26
OL,17,Fappearances for Trinidad & Tobago's
OL,18,Fnational team.
