OL,3,CNUFC legend Shaka Hislop reveals
OL,4,C'aggressive' prostate cancer battle
OL,6,FSince his retirement Shaka now lives
OL,7,Fin the USA, where he also played for
OL,8,FFC Dallas across 10 appearances.
OL,10,FIn a video on social media, the 56-
OL,11,Fyear-old said the "aggressive cancer"
OL,12,Fwas discovered after he insisted on a
OL,13,FPSA test which is used to detect signs
OL,14,Fof prostate cancer.
OL,16,FThis was then confirmed by further
OL,17,Fmedical exams, and he received
OL,18,Ftreatment including a radical
OL,19,Fprostatectomy.
