OL,3,CNUFC legend Shaka Hislop reveals
OL,4,C'aggressive' prostate cancer battle
OL,6,FSince then, further tests revealed the
OL,7,Fcancer had spread to his pelvis. Shaka
OL,8,Ftold fans he recently finishing a
OL,9,Fradiotherapy treatment plan.
OL,11,FThe former Magpie said: "Roughly 18
OL,12,Fmonths ago, I went for my annual
OL,13,Fphysical and insisted on a PSA test,
OL,14,Fas I always do.
OL,16,F"This time, though, my PSA was
OL,17,Felevated and MRI and biopsy quickly
OL,18,Fdetermined that I had a fairly
OL,19,Faggressive prostate cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
