OL,3,CNUFC legend Shaka Hislop reveals
OL,4,C'aggressive' prostate cancer battle
OL,6,F"A year ago, almost to the day,
OL,7,FDecember 6th to be exact, I had a
OL,8,Fradical prostatectomy - and I thought
OL,9,Fthat was it. But then, six months
OL,10,Flater, my PSA was again on the rise
OL,11,Fand another scan showed that my
OL,12,Fprostate cancer had spread to my
OL,13,Fpelvic bone.
OL,15,F"I started on medication pretty soon
OL,16,Fafter - and just this morning
OL,17,Fcompleted seven and a half weeks of
OL,18,Fradiation therapy. The journey
OL,19,Fcontinues."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
