OL,4,C'aggressive' prostate cancer battle
OL,6,FThe prostate specific antigen (PSA)
OL,7,Ftest is a blood test that can help
OL,8,Fdiagnose prostate problems including
OL,9,Fprostate cancer.
OL,11,FIn the UK, routine PSA testing is not
OL,12,Foffered on the NHS, however patients
OL,13,Fmay be offered a PSA test if a doctor
OL,14,Fthinks symptoms exist that could be
OL,15,Fprostate cancer.
OL,17,FThe NHS website states patients who
OL,18,Fare having treatment for a prostate
OL,19,Fcondition may be offered regular PSA
OL,20,Ftests to check how the treatment is
OL,21,Fworking.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
